title: Frigidaire 18 inch Dishwasher FFBD1821 Overview
description:

Features:

Stainless Steel Interior
Premium stainless steel interior for maximum durability.
Multiple-Cycle Options
Features easy-to-use cleaning cycle options including China & Crystal and Heavy Wash.
Quiet Dishwasher
A quiet performance every time.
Delay Start
Set your dishwasher to run on your schedule.
Ready-Select Controls

Energy Saver Dry Option

Low-Rinse Aid Indicator Light
Control Lock Option
China / Crystal Cycle
For a truly gentle cleaning action the China / Crystal Cycle reduces wash pressure by 30 for a thorough cleaning of your most delicate stemware.
